<p class="indent1" style="-uslm-lc:I12" xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:dcterms="http://purl.org/dc/terms/" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">For purposes of paragraph (2)(B), the basis (for purposes of determining gain) of property held by a private foundation on <date date="1969-12-31">December 31, 1969</date>, and continuously thereafter to the date of its disposition, shall be deemed to be not less than the fair market value of such property on <date date="1969-12-31">December 31, 1969</date>.</p>
